 Omelet - custom Raspberry Pi 4 kernel + image with opencode baked in.

 * WiFi:       run `wifi` to scan, pick a network and log in
 * AI agent:   run `opencode` in any project dir
 * API keys:   put provider keys in /etc/omelet/api-keys (then re-login)
               e.g.  export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
 * Auth login: or run `opencode auth login` once to store credentials

